snippet.title: Johnny Depp | Body Language explained | Guilty or Not?
snippet.description:
Welcome to the next episode in the unscripted look at Body Language analysis and Deduction. 
Here you will know about body language and psychology. In This video, I've explained deeply about body language.
The follow up to the Amber Heard analysis. Breaking down what can be read from Johnny Depp's short piece regarding an injury.
